title: Autumn Glass Pumpkin - Orange
description:
Delicate, graceful hand-blown glass breathes life into a beloved icon of the fall season.  Spots of pearlescent ivory and gold, and a stem falling into curly tendrils add character to this glistening pumpkin in shades of orange and gold.  Made exclusively in the USA, and individually signed by the artist, no two are alike.  

9 x 8 1/2 in. diam.
